Avantry
	Provider of broadband wireless optical network services. The company offers transmission product line, ranging from low to high capacity, integrating microwave radio and optical transport systems aimed at carrying flexible combinations of SDH, PDH voice and data and ethernet traffic.
	['', 'transmission product', ' ', 'data transmission', ' ', 'information technology', '']
LiquidLight
	Developer of intelligent optical networking technology that spans from the core to the edge of the optical network. The company offers robust set of revenue enhancing services, such as high-speed internet access, streaming video and guaranteed performance for hosted applications, to the OSP\'s business customers that sit at the edge of the optical network.
	['', 'optical networking', ' ', 'high-speed internet', ' ', 'video streaming', '']
Caliopa
	Developer of optical transceivers for the data and telecommunication markets. The company is a spin-off of the Photonics Research Group of Ghent University and imec.
